Objective
---------

x Setup development environment
x Version control (git)
x Deployment workflow

Application Requirements
------------------------

x Title: TylerMovieManager (Tyler Movie Manager)
x Create movie model:
    x title `str` (1-50 characters)
    x format `choice` (["VHS", "DVD", "Streaming"])
    x length `int` displayed as "x hr yy m" (wut)
    x year `int` (between 1800 and 2100)
    x rating `int` default:null (1-5)
        x Model / Database
        x Seed Database
        x Validation Layer
x CRUD API for a movie collection
    x RESTful responses
x Front-end bootstrap + vue.js 2.0
    x Splash page with cool graphic at / -> /movies for collection
    x Header [Home, Movies] + Footer
    x Responsive Design
    x Movies sortable by: title, format, etc.

Deployment
----------
x Use docker
    x only the .env file should be needed
        x Harden the server (basics, sshd, ufw, fail2ban, rkhunter)
    x Digital Ocean
x Use git hook

Extra
-----

x Users model + oauth
x SPA transitions
x Integrate 3rd party API